1.0.0.name: connect20/Ds_Resposiveslider
1.0.0.description: Ds Responsive Slider is simple jquery library extension and is one of the few fully responsive image slider for Magento which gives a lot of features in admin to configure the slider witout any coding needed for creating easy responsive slider and organize your images and show as slider with effect.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
